5
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:45,700
posebno pokazno friziranje,
dame i gospodo...

6
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:47,660
Raymond Robertson.

7
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:53,540
Lanjski pobjednik dravnog
frizerskog prvenstva,

8
00:01:53,780 --> 00:01:56,460
i mnogih prvenstava prije,
a kad ve nabrajam,

9
00:01:56,540 --> 00:01:59,740
i nagrade za trajnu
frizuru 1978. I 1979. G.

10
00:02:04,580 --> 00:02:09,020
Redkenov salon stoljea,
drugoplasirani 1995.

11
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:15,460
lan meunarodne ekipe na
prvenstvu u feniranju 1998.

12
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,700
Raymond Robertson.

13
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:21,300
Gospodo, dame,

14
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:24,700
objavit u vijest koja
e zauvijek izmijeniti

15
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:28,540
imid ovoga grada.
Neto nalik prevratu.

16
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:31,460
I to onom pravom, Stanley.

17
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:36,820
Pozdravimo Raya Robertsona!

18
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:43,700
Dame i gospodo,

19
00:02:43,900 --> 00:02:49,300
danas, kao predsjednik
londonskog saveza frizera...

20
00:02:50,220 --> 00:02:55,380
Bravo. -Ponosno objavljujem
da je sretan grad domain

21
00:02:55,620 --> 00:02:59,460
ovogodinjeg prvenstva...

22
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:07,220
Keighley! -Kao
gradonaelnik Keighleyja,

23
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:11,140
ponosno objavljujem da je
s dugog popisa kandidata

24
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:16,220
na gradi izabran
za domaina, samo malo...

25
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:21,820
Ovogodinjeg dravnog
frizerskog prvenstva!

26
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:26,420
Kako, molim?

27
00:03:26,660 --> 00:03:31,100
Ovogodinjeg dravnog
frizerskog prvenstva.

28
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,740
Pardon.

29
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:41,980
Dogaa se. -To je to?

30
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:45,260
Friziranje? Zaustavite
tiskanje zadnje stranice.

31
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:48,020
Dajte, momci...

32
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:51,300
To natjecanje promijenit
e izgled naega grada.

33
00:03:51,580 --> 00:03:53,300
Gadovi nezahvalni.

34
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:54,780
Zaalit ete.

35
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:58,380
Tony, je li natjecanje
otvorenog tipa? -Nije.

36
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:02,220
Samo za profesionalce.
-Ja sam profesionalac.

37
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:11,300
Buenje, ljubavi.

38
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:15,820
Koliko puta moram rei?

39
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:19,660
Prljave izme ostavljaj dolje!

40
00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:27,740
aj! -U ajniku je!

41
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:35,460
Prema scenariju Nikad
bolje Simona Beaufoya

42
00:04:37,380 --> 00:04:38,700
Shelley!

43
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:42,100
Sretno, ljubavi.

44
00:04:49,380 --> 00:04:52,380
Ma nema anse, Tony.
-Ma daj, Phile...

45
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:54,860
Mogao bi pobijediti. -Ne.

46
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:57,860
ali se? Nee se prijaviti?

47
00:04:58,380 --> 00:05:00,740
Pa kralj si zanata! Br. 1!

48
00:05:01,020 --> 00:05:03,140
Miruj. Da ti ne odreem uho.

49
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:07,660
A ti nemoj buljiti s toliko
zanimanja. -Pa kad vas ujem.

50
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:10,900
To je ekipno natjecanje.
Zamisli, Phile,

51
00:05:11,100 --> 00:05:13,300
otac i sin u ekipi.
Brian je za.

52
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:16,660
Sluaj, deset sam se godina
natjecao. Nisam trebao.

53
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:19,260
Brija sam. Kao
i on. I gotovo.

54
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:22,260
Skratit u je sa svih
strana i gotov si.

55
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:26,380
Pobijedili bismo kao
od ale, tata. -Dosta.

56
00:05:36,620 --> 00:05:38,020
Naprijed.

57
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:41,700
Zdravo.

58
00:05:53,780 --> 00:05:56,660
Go Birkett... Shelley...

59
00:05:57,900 --> 00:05:59,380
Roberte...

60
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:14,020
Da ponem ja? -Molim?

61
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:17,860
Ja u zapoeti, moe? Dobro...

62
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:21,700
Da vidim mogu li se
prisjetiti svega.

63
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:26,180
Da. Moemo dalje
na nekoliko naina.

64
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:31,740
Naravno, tu je kemoterapija,
no to bi vam bila ve trea.

65
00:06:33,020 --> 00:06:37,020
Previe je to recidiva.

66
00:06:37,420 --> 00:06:40,900
Tu je i mogunost
presaivanja kotane sri,

67
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:45,020
vjerojatna koliko
i dolazak Pape na tulama.

68
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:49,780
Zato, bez okolianja,
proivjeli ste svoje.

69
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,660
Gotovi ste.

70
00:06:53,100 --> 00:06:55,180
Shelley... -Imam li pravo?

71
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:58,700
Kemoterapija... -Daj,
Roberte, imam li pravo?

72
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:05,140
Ima.

73
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:19,860
Super je kad ima pravo, ha?

74
00:07:26,500 --> 00:07:28,220
Jesi dobro, ljubavi?

75
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:31,300
Mama. -Ima asak?

76
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:35,580
Pa zna...
-Moramo razgovarati.

77
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:37,660
Navratit e poslije?

78
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:41,740
Moda. -Veeras?
Skuhat u neto.

79
00:07:42,820 --> 00:07:45,740
Ne mogu veeras,
radim. -Sutra?

80
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:48,380
Nazvat u te, moe?

81
00:07:49,460 --> 00:07:51,540
Mogao bi i viknuti, ula bih.

82
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:53,140
Da...

83
00:07:54,620 --> 00:08:00,020
uj, loe je volje.
Moram... Pa-pa. -Da.

84
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:14,740
Nemojte mi umrijeti ispod.

85
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:19,220
Malen korak za vas,
ali velik za ovjeanstvo.

86
00:08:25,020 --> 00:08:27,860
I? -Sve u redu.

87
00:08:29,020 --> 00:08:31,380
100%? -Da.

88
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:35,500
To se trai! Sjajno.

89
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:39,220
JO MALO PA STRIU!

90
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:09,660
Budi tako dobar, Vincente.
Upravo sam nalakirala nokte.

91
00:09:11,260 --> 00:09:14,780
Molimo da ne uzimate suila
za kosu iz hotelskih soba.

92
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:18,940
elim da Christina bude
sa mnom. Publiciteta radi.

93
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:22,140
Prijavi nas, Louise.
-Vrlo rado. -Hvala.

94
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:26,740
Tako, ljubavi. Samo stoj
uz mene, neka te dobro vide.

95
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:31,740
Vidi li one lakrdijae?
Kilburn Kutters. Braa.

96
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:35,380
Jasmine je udana za
Roberta. Uasno je teka.

97
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:37,100
Ali je krasan model.

98
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:40,180
Chris, ime tretira kosu?

99
00:09:40,420 --> 00:09:43,260
Ne znam. Onime to naem
u ormariu. -Ti se to...?

100
00:09:44,260 --> 00:09:47,020
ali se? -alim,
i mama upotrebljava isto.

101
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:51,220
Ali vie nisi s njom u
Minneapolisu, ve sa mnom.

102
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:55,460
I neto mora shvatiti.
Natjecanje je ve poelo.

103
00:09:55,700 --> 00:09:59,220
Tata, dugo te nisam vidjela.
Na praznicima sam.

104
00:09:59,380 --> 00:10:01,740
Ti si traio mene da ti
budem model, a ne ja tebe.

105
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,700
Ne, sve je puno.

106
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:08,300
Ali davno smo rezervirali.
-U knjizi ne pie nita.

107
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:12,940
Ba me briga za knjigu,
duice. elim nae sobe!

108
00:10:13,220 --> 00:10:16,340
Nemamo slobodnih
soba. Puni smo.

109
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:19,140
Klju, g. TJ!

110
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:22,820
Apartman Randolph.

111
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:25,500
Popalio nam je sobe! Gad!

112
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:30,500
On je stari gad.
I dao je svoje.

113
00:10:31,260 --> 00:10:34,860
Ne, jest. Ba me
briga to kau drugi.

114
00:10:35,500 --> 00:10:40,220
Osvojio je neke nagrade,
dobro. Ali davno.

115
00:10:40,420 --> 00:10:44,140
Kad su Jetiji hodali ulicama
i traili frizerski salon.

116
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:49,060
Danas je drugo vrijeme, stari.

117
00:10:50,660 --> 00:10:53,700
Moderno friziranje
slinije je kiparstvu.

118
00:10:53,980 --> 00:10:57,900
Da se Henry Moore rodi danas,
ne bi se zafrkavao s mramorom.

119
00:10:58,420 --> 00:11:00,100
Bio bi frizer.

120
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:03,940
S kim to razgovara?

121
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,860
S g. Barryjem Birtom.

122
00:11:09,060 --> 00:11:13,020
Izvolite, g. Birt. Sretno.

123
00:11:16,660 --> 00:11:19,300
Rekli su da imamo sree jer se
upravo otvorilo jedno mjesto.

124
00:11:19,540 --> 00:11:22,580
Nije ni udo. U zabiti smo.
-Kau da im je doruak dobar.

125
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:24,980
ali se, zar ne? -Ovaj
je posljednji s popisa.

126
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:26,860
Moe spavati u autu.

127
00:11:27,940 --> 00:11:29,460
Oprosti, duo.

128
00:11:47,780 --> 00:11:49,180
to?

129
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:11,500
Oev ujak Barton. 93 g.

130
00:12:12,060 --> 00:12:13,540
Nepua.

131
00:12:13,860 --> 00:12:16,460
Izloit e tijelo preksutra.

132
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:25,980
Uite ako elite. Ima mjesta.
Ba smo dobili jo jednu sobu.

133
00:12:26,900 --> 00:12:30,580
Krasno. Tako,
Barbara. Tako, sve.

134
00:12:31,180 --> 00:12:34,540
Sad pruajte ruke.

135
00:12:35,780 --> 00:12:39,580
Prokleta gaerobika. -Aerobika.

136
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:43,500
U svojim godinama zvat
u ga kako god hou.

137
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:47,540
utljiva si. to te mui?

138
00:12:48,220 --> 00:12:51,020
Ja sam frizerka, Daisy.
Nita me ne mui.

139
00:12:51,620 --> 00:12:55,060
Nalazi su ti trebali biti
gotovi ovaj tjedan. Zar ne?

140
00:12:56,380 --> 00:13:01,900
I? -Sve je u redu. ista sam.

141
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:05,580
Zato plae, zar ne?

142
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:08,260
Mislila sam da ste slijepi.

143
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:12,220
I jesam. Suze ti
lijevaju po meni.

144
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:16,420
Oprostite. -Doi.

145
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:19,300
Ne preputaj mu se.

146
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:23,700
Ve jesam, Daisy.

147
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:26,140
Sigurno nisi.

148
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:32,300
Sluaj, dugo sam
razmiljala o smrti.

149
00:13:32,540 --> 00:13:35,940
Ima jedna prednost
kad zna da e umrijeti.

150
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:38,500
Moe rijeiti neke stvari.

151
00:13:39,020 --> 00:13:41,260
Ja to s Harryjem nisam mogla.

152
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:46,940
Jednoga je trenutka hranio
maku i pripremao pivo,

153
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:51,460
a onda ga vie
nije bilo. Umro je.

154
00:13:52,620 --> 00:13:58,060
Nisam se oprostila s njim.
Toliko nedovrenih stvari.

155
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:04,340
Ti si rijeila
sve svoje stvari?

156
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:08,140
Svakako, Daisy.

157
00:14:08,340 --> 00:14:11,460
Sa svojim bivim muem
ne razgovaram ve 10 g.,

158
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:14,980
sin me se srami,

159
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:20,580
a cura misli da nam je najvei
problem izbor boje za salon.

160
00:14:22,660 --> 00:14:25,220
Mislim da nemam
nedovrenih poslova.

161
00:14:25,380 --> 00:14:28,900
Onda ti je to dobro dolo, ha?

162
00:14:31,860 --> 00:14:33,660
Fantastino!

163
00:14:34,060 --> 00:14:36,620
Otkud vam?
-S kolodvora u Leedsu.

164
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:39,860
Obnavljaju ga. Nije
bio skup. I radi.

165
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:53,380
Dobro. Vrlo dobro.

166
00:14:55,140 --> 00:14:56,940
Hvala, momci. Vidimo se.

167
00:14:59,580 --> 00:15:01,580
Jesi dobro, Shelley?

168
00:15:01,820 --> 00:15:04,020
Budi sjeanja, zar ne?

169
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:10,340
Najvie sam voljela Veernje
frizure dok sam bila model.

170
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:14,100
Phil je kreirao
nevjerojatne frizure.

171
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:16,460
S velikim kosturima.

172
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:20,580
Onda se pouri. Prijave
se primaju do sutra naveer.

173
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:25,460
Deset godina prekasno, Tony.
-I Phil je rekao isto.

174
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:29,860
Zna li da se ne natjee
nijedna ekipa iz Keighleyja?

175
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:34,020
A domaini smo! Ba tipino.

176
00:15:34,340 --> 00:15:37,660
Imamo frizera i modela
koji su veterani,

177
00:15:37,860 --> 00:15:41,020
Brian radi kao frizer,
a Sandra kao model.

178
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:46,180
I to uinite kad nam
u grad doe cirkus? Gledate!

179
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:50,620
Phil i ja ne razgovaramo. -Ne
traim od vas da razgovarate.

180
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,740
Traim od vas da iate.

181
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:34,940
Christina.

182
00:16:35,780 --> 00:16:38,340
Tako. Ne zaboravi korijene.

183
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:42,620
Ako ti se svidi, dopustit e
da bojim kosu tvojim modelima?

184
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:44,820
Moda. Ali samo moda.

185
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:48,140
to je u ovoj mjeavini?
Meni ne izgleda najbolje.

186
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:50,700
Meni se ini dobra.

187
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:53,100
Dobro moe proi
u salonu tvoje mame,

188
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:55,300
ali morat e to malo bolje
ako eli bojiti za mene.

189
00:16:55,500 --> 00:16:58,220
Dobro ne donosi pobjedu.
-Prui mi priliku, tata.

190
00:16:58,540 --> 00:17:03,020
Dobar sam kolorist. -Ja to
ne kuim. To je samo kosa.

191
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:16,140
Samo kosa?

192
00:17:16,780 --> 00:17:19,740
Mnogo se toga moe
zakljuiti prema kosi.

193
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:22,020
Aha? -Aha.

194
00:17:22,620 --> 00:17:24,220
Na primjer...

195
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:28,540
Oprao si je prije tri dana.

196
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:35,100
TTST. -Tea-Tree
Scalp Treatmentom.

197
00:17:35,300 --> 00:17:40,580
A iana je, i to prilino
dobro, prije dva i pol tjedna.

198
00:17:44,020 --> 00:17:45,340
to?

199
00:17:47,620 --> 00:17:50,500
iao te Phil Allen.
-Kako znate?

200
00:17:51,340 --> 00:17:54,460
Phil? On jo ia?
-Tko je Phil?

201
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:58,420
Vidi ovo? Mali vrak
na zatiljku? Nepogreivo.

202
00:17:58,580 --> 00:18:00,740
Vie se ne natjee.
Ve godinama.

203
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:02,500
Tko je on? -Nitko.

204
00:18:37,900 --> 00:18:42,660
Sandra, ula si za
frizersko natjecanje?

205
00:18:44,060 --> 00:18:47,460
Da se prijavimo?
-Ti to ozbiljno?

206
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:52,740
Da. -Ne znam, Shell.

207
00:18:53,260 --> 00:18:56,500
Bilo je to davno. Teko da
bih mogla proi kao model.

208
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:59,660
Ima krasnu kosu. I zna to.

209
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:03,020
Nagovorit emo Briana
da ia mukarce,

210
00:19:03,740 --> 00:19:06,140
a Phil e preuzeti
cjeloviti imid.

211
00:19:08,060 --> 00:19:10,700
Brian i Phil?

212
00:19:12,260 --> 00:19:15,660
Zato ne? -Daj, Shell, koliko
razloga protiv da ti nabrojim?

213
00:19:15,860 --> 00:19:18,820
Moe ovaj: Bila si udana za
njega. Ja sam mu bila model.

214
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:21,980
Pobjegle smo zajedno veer
uoi dravnoga prvenstva.

215
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:25,220
Nemoj. -Ve gotovo 10 g.
nije mi rekao ni rije.

216
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:30,140
Kao ni ti njemu. Vrijeme
je da prekinete s time.

217
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:32,580
Ma je li?

218
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:38,340
Sandra! Mislila sam da e
biti za. -Ne kaem da nisam.

219
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:43,220
Ali ako to kanimo uiniti,
zar ne moemo bez njega? -Ne.

220
00:19:44,220 --> 00:19:49,100
Iskreno, prije bi me skratio
za glavu nego mi skratio kosu.

221
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:57,100
Ali voljela bih pokuati
jo jedanput. Zbilja bih.

222
00:20:00,580 --> 00:20:05,460
Izvadi kreme. Bit u
najstarija na pozornici.

223
00:20:22,180 --> 00:20:25,260
Dobro izgleda. Dobro.

224
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:34,100
Za nas.

225
00:20:38,740 --> 00:20:40,820
Sigurna si da to
nije regenerator?

226
00:20:44,300 --> 00:20:47,260
Ukusniji je ako ste
pijani i leite u krevetu.

227
00:20:51,260 --> 00:20:53,100
Odmah dolazim.

228
00:20:56,660 --> 00:20:58,020
Da...

229
00:20:59,220 --> 00:21:00,780
Za nas.

230
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:41,020
Sjednite, odmah dolazim.
Briane, u radnju!

231
00:21:46,860 --> 00:21:50,420
Dola si u posjet?
-Samo elim razgovarati.

232
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:55,940
Briane! -S tobom. Molim te.

233
00:22:01,860 --> 00:22:03,340
Zdravo, Briane.

234
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:05,300
Mama?

235
00:22:06,540 --> 00:22:09,580
ujte, znam da je suludo,

236
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:13,500
ali prijavit u
se za natjecanje.

237
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:15,980
Pitala sam se...

238
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:18,540
to kaete?

239
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:21,860
Iz svakog grada moe
sudjelovati po jedan salon.

240
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:24,300
Nitko se iz Keighleyja
nije prijavio.

241
00:22:24,540 --> 00:22:28,860
Mi smo na neki nain salon.
Mogli bismo biti. Tehniki.

242
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:33,780
Provjerila sam u pravilima.
Obitelj smo. -Tehniki.

243
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:38,500
Mogli bismo. Malo bi nam
trebalo da se vratimo u igru.

244
00:22:39,740 --> 00:22:41,660
Kao u stara vremena.

245
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:46,820
Ona su zavrila prije 10 g.
kad si digla sidro i otila.

246
00:22:51,020 --> 00:22:53,540
Dorukovao si? Otvaramo.

247
00:22:55,940 --> 00:22:59,180
Briane? to kae?

248
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:02,220
Molim te...

249
00:23:03,300 --> 00:23:04,980
Samo izvoli.

250
00:23:06,460 --> 00:23:08,420
Biraj, mome.

251
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:20,020
Ta ti je dobra. Jo
jedna u nizu, rekla bih.

252
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:29,940
Zaboga... Christina!

253
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:34,860
Treba te jedinica
za bioloko ratovanje.

254
00:23:43,780 --> 00:23:47,860
Treba mi jo malo vjebe.
-Louise, ti boji.

255
00:23:52,100 --> 00:23:55,180
Bilo bi bolje da imam ive
modele za vjebanje, zar ne?

256
00:24:07,620 --> 00:24:11,700
Jedna od najgorih kosa
koje sam imao nesreu iati.

257
00:24:11,900 --> 00:24:14,660
Kako su nisko pali velikani.

258
00:24:15,820 --> 00:24:17,700
Zar ne, Phile?

259
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:22,860
ianje je 7,50 funta.
S pranjem stoji 9,50.

260
00:24:24,780 --> 00:24:27,700
Sjajno. 7,50.

261
00:24:28,140 --> 00:24:30,940
Nalazim se u muzeju.
-Izai moe besplatno.

262
00:24:31,140 --> 00:24:36,100
Daj, Phile. Ja bih
se trebao ljutiti.

263
00:24:37,340 --> 00:24:40,260
Tko je komu oteo modela?
-To je prolost, Ray.

264
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:42,900
Kao da govori
o nekomu posve drugom.

265
00:24:43,300 --> 00:24:48,220
Onda sutra neemo vidjeti
munjevite kare na djelu? -Ne.

266
00:24:48,660 --> 00:24:51,620
teta. Ove godine
lovim trei naslov.

267
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:59,420
Pobijedim li, osvojit u ovo.
Zauvijek. Nije li to sjajno?

268
00:25:00,460 --> 00:25:02,980
Jest, ako voli srebrninu.

269
00:25:03,660 --> 00:25:06,780
Pitam se bi li ti
osvojio trei naslov

270
00:25:07,460 --> 00:25:13,340
da Sandra nije pobjegla
sa Shelley. -Ne izazivaj.

271
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:21,020
ao mi je to te
nisam uspio nagovoriti.

272
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:28,740
OTVORENJE

273
00:25:29,460 --> 00:25:31,340
Oprostite!

274
00:25:32,100 --> 00:25:34,180
to radi na Noinoj
farmi? -Molim?

275
00:25:37,780 --> 00:25:40,020
Ti si Christina, zar ne?

276
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:44,180
Briane! Ti!

277
00:25:44,420 --> 00:25:47,380
Kako si?

278
00:25:47,940 --> 00:25:51,060
Nije loe. A ti?

279
00:25:51,700 --> 00:25:53,580
Dobro sam.

280
00:25:53,820 --> 00:25:57,060
Jesi li... -Ti... Model si?

281
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:59,140
Da.

282
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:03,580
I bojila sam, ali sam
zabrljala neke vlasulje

283
00:26:03,860 --> 00:26:07,420
pa mi tata vie
ne da pa... A ti?

284
00:26:10,980 --> 00:26:15,020
iam u tatinoj radnji,
ali... Ne na natjecanjima.

285
00:26:22,380 --> 00:26:24,220
Promijenila si se.

286
00:26:29,580 --> 00:26:31,220
Dame i gospodo...

287
00:26:32,620 --> 00:26:36,100
Divno je vidjeti toliko
razliitih ljudi veeras.

288
00:26:36,580 --> 00:26:41,660
Ovdje su ekipe iz svih krajeva
Ujedinjenog Kraljevstva.

289
00:26:41,900 --> 00:26:45,060
Da bi osvojili trofej
Srebrne kare,

290
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:50,940
ovi velikani frizerskoga posla
borit e se u 4 discipline.

291
00:26:51,260 --> 00:26:52,860
To su:

292
00:26:54,500 --> 00:26:59,060
ensko feniranje,
muki slobodni stil,

293
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:03,340
u kojemu e modeli
biti publika.

294
00:27:04,100 --> 00:27:08,460
Veernje frizure,
tj. Frizure za izlazak,

295
00:27:08,780 --> 00:27:15,020
te cjeloviti imid,
spoj kose i metafizike.

296
00:27:16,100 --> 00:27:21,860
Ali upamtite, svi natjecatelji
moraju se pridravati pravila.

297
00:27:22,060 --> 00:27:23,780
Samo sanjaj.

298
00:27:24,780 --> 00:27:28,460
Primjerak pravilnika nai ete
u torbi ispred svojih vrata.

299
00:27:28,620 --> 00:27:31,580
Sve prijave moraju
stii do ponoi.

300
00:27:31,940 --> 00:27:35,860
Ne ekajte, nego doite.

301
00:27:40,540 --> 00:27:41,940
Pogledajte ih.

302
00:27:42,340 --> 00:27:45,540
Meo sam bolje frizure
s poda naega salona.

303
00:27:46,140 --> 00:27:48,700
Idem u krevet. Ti?

304
00:27:49,020 --> 00:27:50,860
Ostat u jo malo.

305
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:53,660
Dok ne popijem pie.
-Kako hoe.

306
00:27:54,020 --> 00:27:56,220
uvaj je. -Dobro.

307
00:27:58,580 --> 00:28:01,420
Zdravo. -Bog, stari.
Drago mi je to te vidim.

308
00:28:01,540 --> 00:28:03,500
Sve je u redu. Phil se
nije prijavio. -Naravno.

309
00:28:03,700 --> 00:28:06,020
Ve se 10 g. Ne natjee.
-Svejedno sam provjerio.

310
00:28:06,180 --> 00:28:08,700
Ne elim da mi ita upropasti
stvar ovaj put. Ima eljeve?

311
00:28:11,100 --> 00:28:14,100
Rijeeno. -Gdje je Christina?

312
00:28:25,380 --> 00:28:27,580
Hajde, duo. Idemo.
Sutra je velik dan.

313
00:28:27,820 --> 00:28:29,500
Tata, ovo je Brian. Sjea se?

314
00:28:30,180 --> 00:28:32,700
Da, vidio sam vas u salonu.

315
00:28:33,020 --> 00:28:34,420
Salonu?

316
00:28:37,540 --> 00:28:39,900
Tvoj je otac neko
bio netko i neto.

317
00:28:40,220 --> 00:28:42,420
Sad se boji i prijaviti.

318
00:28:42,820 --> 00:28:44,420
Ali ja se ne bojim.

319
00:28:44,620 --> 00:28:46,180
Junior, ha?

320
00:28:46,620 --> 00:28:49,900
Christina. -Uzet u taksi.
Vidimo se poslije.

321
00:28:55,260 --> 00:28:57,420
Zar nisi rekao da
se nee prijaviti?

322
00:28:58,580 --> 00:28:59,900
Jesam.

323
00:29:16,580 --> 00:29:18,860
Bila je to zgodna ideja.

324
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:21,540
Uvijek postoji drugi put.

325
00:29:27,860 --> 00:29:29,940
Briane, otkud ti ovdje?

326
00:29:31,820 --> 00:29:35,420
Ne iam za tebe inae,
ve samo na natjecanju.

327
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:39,420
to kae? Jesi za?

328
00:29:40,700 --> 00:29:42,500
Naravno da jesam.

329
00:29:44,220 --> 00:29:45,740
Sandra?

330
00:29:50,420 --> 00:29:51,780
To.

331
00:29:53,980 --> 00:29:56,900
Sredi kosu ako eli
da te sutra iam.

332
00:29:57,140 --> 00:29:59,860
Regenerator
ili osovinsko ulje.

333
00:30:00,220 --> 00:30:01,780
Ne zapoinji!

334
00:30:03,180 --> 00:30:06,020
Ne bismo smjeli razgovarati.
Tata e me ubiti.

335
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:07,820
Nee saznati.

336
00:30:08,260 --> 00:30:13,420
Treba vjebati, a i ja moram
razgibati prste za sutra pa...

337
00:30:13,780 --> 00:30:15,620
Da, ali...

338
00:30:16,340 --> 00:30:18,100
Sranje, Briane!

339
00:30:21,220 --> 00:30:22,900
Jo nikad...

340
00:30:23,820 --> 00:30:26,300
Nikad nisam vidjela mrtvaca.

341
00:30:26,500 --> 00:30:29,820
Bar ne uivo i izbliza.

342
00:30:30,740 --> 00:30:32,940
Kosa raste i kad umre, zna.

343
00:30:33,380 --> 00:30:36,460
Jezivo. Kosa i nokti.

344
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:40,460
Ovo je ujak Barton. Mislim
da spava u njegovom krevetu.

345
00:30:43,140 --> 00:30:44,900
Smeta li ti to?

346
00:30:47,820 --> 00:30:52,500
Pomalo. Nemaju punou ni
vrstou. U tome je problem.

347
00:30:53,220 --> 00:30:56,700
Rabim regenerator za punou.
To malo pomae.

348
00:30:58,860 --> 00:31:01,940
to kae? Pita se
hoe li se boja primiti?

349
00:31:09,460 --> 00:31:11,060
Isuse!

350
00:31:11,500 --> 00:31:13,900
Uredi me. -to?

351
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:17,140
elim da me uredi.
-Sutra. to bi jo htjela?

352
00:31:17,300 --> 00:31:18,700
Ne to.

353
00:31:22,580 --> 00:31:24,220
Ovo.

354
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:29,340
U obliku srca. -Jas...

355
00:31:29,620 --> 00:31:31,260
Ne smijem.

356
00:31:32,300 --> 00:31:36,420
to e Robert pomisliti
ako vidi muf u obliku srca?

357
00:31:38,340 --> 00:31:42,700
Sluaj, za njega je
to Bermudski trokut.

358
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:44,740
Ako je eli...

359
00:31:47,100 --> 00:31:48,780
Oiaj je.

360
00:31:57,340 --> 00:31:59,380
Tata ti zbilja ne da da boji?

361
00:31:59,620 --> 00:32:04,540
Ne razumijem. Godinama sam
vjebala s Deaconom kod mame.

362
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,740
Deacon?

363
00:32:07,340 --> 00:32:10,060
Moj deko. Recimo.

364
00:32:12,740 --> 00:32:15,260
Recimo? -Da...

365
00:32:18,180 --> 00:32:20,820
Dobro, pourimo se.

366
00:32:20,980 --> 00:32:23,500
Moramo mu vratiti
prijanji izgled do jutra.

367
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:27,620
Pomozi mi. Sredit emo njega,
a onda i ujaka Bartona.

368
00:32:30,020 --> 00:32:31,940
Uvijek si bio udan.

369
00:32:32,460 --> 00:32:34,100
Nedostajao si mi.

370
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:36,180
Bilo ti je samo 7 g.

371
00:32:36,900 --> 00:32:38,700
Svejedno si mi nedostajao.

372
00:32:40,020 --> 00:32:44,060
I ti meni, Christina.
I ti meni.

373
00:32:49,580 --> 00:32:52,220
Chris! Samo sam te poljubio!

374
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:57,620
Christina, ja... -On je iv!

375
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:02,220
To je samo zaostali
zrak u grkljanu.

376
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:04,140
ula sam ga. Zahroptao je.

377
00:33:04,380 --> 00:33:07,460
Ui, ut e te ljudi.
-Ne idem natrag unutra.

378
00:33:07,660 --> 00:33:09,420
To je samo zrak.

379
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,980
Doi, pokazat u ti.

380
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:28,900
O, ne.

381
00:33:31,020 --> 00:33:32,500
O, ne!

382
00:33:33,020 --> 00:33:36,540
Izloit e ujaka Bartona
u 10. Gotov sam.

383
00:33:37,780 --> 00:33:42,300
Mrtav sam. Odvest u te kui.

384
00:34:00,940 --> 00:34:02,540
Zakljuano je, kvragu.

385
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:24,500
Izgleda kao Sid Vicious!

386
00:34:32,460 --> 00:34:36,020
Hajde, Briane.
Nemoj me iznevjeriti.

387
00:34:39,220 --> 00:34:42,780
Gdje si dosad? -Oprosti.

388
00:34:53,020 --> 00:34:55,300
Nagovarala te, zar ne?

389
00:34:55,860 --> 00:34:57,660
Nema veze s njom.

390
00:34:57,900 --> 00:35:01,580
Zadovoljan si Sandrom kao
modelom? -Nema veze ni s njom.

391
00:35:01,780 --> 00:35:06,140
Nego s ime? -S Rayem.

392
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:11,300
Gazi po tebi,
a ti mu to doputa.

393
00:35:21,420 --> 00:35:23,260
PRVA RUNDA
FENIRANJE

394
00:35:40,460 --> 00:35:42,820
Prepusti ovo meni. Phile!

395
00:35:53,660 --> 00:35:55,300
Dame i gospodo...

396
00:35:55,580 --> 00:35:58,860
Dobrodoli na dravno
frizersko prvenstvo

397
00:35:59,100 --> 00:36:01,380
ovdje u Keighleyju!

398
00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:07,380
Kako hoete.

399
00:36:09,020 --> 00:36:12,340
Frizeri, provjerite
svoja suila za kosu!

400
00:36:22,580 --> 00:36:27,140
Dame i gospodo,
natjecatelji... -Gdje si bio?

401
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:29,020
Tu sam, dobro?

402
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:31,540
Feniranje ena na vrijeme!

403
00:36:40,700 --> 00:36:42,820
Hoemo li poeti? -Da.

404
00:36:43,020 --> 00:36:47,020
Tri, dva, jedan, ponimo!

405
00:36:59,500 --> 00:37:03,060
Isuse, popucali su ti vrhovi.
-Pogledaj malo sebe, duice.

406
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:12,420
Onda? Kako srce?

407
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:14,980
Svrbi.

408
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:18,460
Tata! -Samo se smijei, duo.

409
00:37:18,660 --> 00:37:21,900
Crveni vrhovi su bili pun
pogodak. Svi priaju o tome.

410
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:25,540
Samo sam vjebala. -Na nekima
se vjeba, a na nekima ne.

411
00:37:25,740 --> 00:37:27,940
Mrtvaci spadaju
u ovu drugu kategoriju.

412
00:37:28,180 --> 00:37:32,500
I s nekim se vjeba, a s nekim
ne. A Brian spada u ove druge.

413
00:37:32,660 --> 00:37:35,140
Dobro? -Dobro. Oprosti.

414
00:37:37,500 --> 00:37:39,340
to je ovo?

415
00:37:39,500 --> 00:37:41,620
ekaj malo. ealj mi se topi!

416
00:37:41,940 --> 00:37:44,500
to je ovo? Ne mogu
ovako raditi!

417
00:37:47,180 --> 00:37:51,900
Posluitelju! to je
ovo? Pogledajte ealj!

418
00:37:56,740 --> 00:37:57,820
/teta./

419
00:37:58,700 --> 00:38:00,020
Sue!

420
00:38:10,300 --> 00:38:13,540
Stvarno mi je ao.
-Gotov si? -Moram ii.

421
00:38:14,380 --> 00:38:16,300
Oprostite. -Doi ovamo!

422
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:44,620
Stvarno mi je ao, Saule.
-Natjecatelji, stanite.

423
00:38:44,940 --> 00:38:47,420
Svi natjecatelji
neka prestanu s radom.

424
00:38:47,660 --> 00:38:51,460
Sat je stao. Slijedi
stanka od pet minuta.

425
00:38:51,860 --> 00:38:54,180
Dobit ete nove eljeve.

426
00:38:54,780 --> 00:38:56,860
E jebe ovo.

427
00:38:58,580 --> 00:39:00,980
alim, Phile, morali smo.

428
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:07,380
to je, duo?

429
00:39:08,340 --> 00:39:12,740
Nisu mi ozlijedili
prste. -Budalo. -Hvala.

430
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:17,220
Pravo ti budi. Ja te
neu aliti. -Prestani!

431
00:39:17,420 --> 00:39:20,900
Gdje ti je pamet bila?
Unakaziti mrtvaca!

432
00:39:21,100 --> 00:39:25,340
Trebao bi otii psihijatru.
-Pusti to. -I kloni se Chris.

433
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:31,740
to se to tebe tie? Zna to,
samo si ljubomoran. -Dosta!

434
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:38,180
Prvi put u ivotu trebam
pomo od vas dvojice.

435
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:42,700
Oboavate iati,
ali za mene neete.

436
00:39:47,060 --> 00:39:49,260
Da zbrojim dva i dva?

437
00:39:49,540 --> 00:39:51,540
Trebao bi.

438
00:39:53,820 --> 00:39:57,860
Jesi li... -Kemoterapiju,
zraenje, holistiku masau,

439
00:39:59,180 --> 00:40:03,180
beskorisne pripravke od
pialine kineskih majmuna...

440
00:40:04,340 --> 00:40:06,900
Iskuala sam sve to postoji.

441
00:40:18,340 --> 00:40:22,460
Ti se bar nee moi igrati
mojom kosom kad umrem, duo.

442
00:40:25,860 --> 00:40:30,380
Zato mi nisi rekla? -Zato to
10 g. Ne razgovaramo. Dobro?

443
00:40:37,340 --> 00:40:38,860
Sandra?

444
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:45,180
Jo misli da sam dobro.

445
00:40:47,620 --> 00:40:49,900
eka da mi ponovno naraste.

446
00:40:50,780 --> 00:40:52,780
Ne mogu joj rei.

447
00:40:53,540 --> 00:40:57,740
Rekla si nama. -Jesam.

448
00:40:59,020 --> 00:41:04,220
Zato to vam
zapravo nije stalo.

449
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:09,340
Njoj je toliko stalo da bi
joj srce puklo. Krava blesava.

450
00:41:09,540 --> 00:41:13,860
Natjecatelji mogu nastaviti.
Imate jo 15 minuta.

451
00:41:15,500 --> 00:41:17,420
Hajde, ljubavi.

452
00:41:23,140 --> 00:41:26,780
Mislila sam da e bar
ti primijetiti vlasulju.

453
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:38,420
Frizeri, vrijeme je isteklo.
Odloite eljeve!

454
00:41:51,820 --> 00:41:55,780
Poinje ocjenjivanje.
Modeli, zauzmite poze.

455
00:42:43,220 --> 00:42:47,300
Na 3. Su mjestu sa 79 bodova

456
00:42:47,900 --> 00:42:50,220
Kilburn Kutters iz Londona.

457
00:43:00,380 --> 00:43:03,340
Na drugom, s 80 bodova

458
00:43:03,540 --> 00:43:06,940
Style Warriors iz Birminghama!

459
00:43:14,100 --> 00:43:19,860
Na prvom je mjestu, s 82 boda

460
00:43:20,260 --> 00:43:24,860
Frizerski studio Raya
Robertsona iz junog Londona!

461
00:43:29,700 --> 00:43:31,900
Maji kaalj. -Jednu
smo obavili. Jo tri.

462
00:43:32,020 --> 00:43:36,060
Druga runda, slobodni stil
za mukarce, sutra je u 10.

463
00:43:36,300 --> 00:43:39,860
Dobrovoljci iz publike
dobit e besplatnu frizuru.

464
00:43:40,060 --> 00:43:44,540
Iz eira e izvlaiti imena
ekipa kojima e biti modeli.

465
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:48,460
MALO BLISTAVIH TRENUTAKA
NA FRIZERSKOM PRVENSTVU

466
00:43:50,500 --> 00:43:52,860
Krasno. Kao nekad.

467
00:43:53,860 --> 00:43:56,660
Zdravo, Phile.
Dva gin-tonika.

468
00:43:56,940 --> 00:43:59,020
Detroit, 1982.

469
00:44:01,020 --> 00:44:03,620
Ne pratim te ba.
-Stari trik s eljevima.

470
00:44:03,900 --> 00:44:08,460
S finala u Detroitu 1982.
Vikali smo prekraj!,

471
00:44:08,700 --> 00:44:14,180
dok su Ameri, iji se eljevi
nisu topili, nastavili raditi.

472
00:44:14,620 --> 00:44:18,020
Nema nagrade ako pogodi
tko je pobijedio te godine.

473
00:44:18,300 --> 00:44:23,900
Nisi to mogao zaboraviti.
-1982... Ne sjeam se.

474
00:44:24,020 --> 00:44:26,340
Napredovali smo otad. Hvala.

475
00:44:26,980 --> 00:44:28,860
Bar veina nas.

476
00:44:42,260 --> 00:44:45,940
Da, eljevi. Namjeteno je,
znamo. Hvala to si se javio.

477
00:44:47,020 --> 00:44:49,940
Ako je namjeteno, ne znai
da se ne moe promijeniti.

478
00:44:53,340 --> 00:44:55,060
Odjenite se.

479
00:45:06,540 --> 00:45:08,820
to radi? -Podvala.

480
00:45:09,260 --> 00:45:11,980
Ray e ga tri sata dotjerivati

481
00:45:12,220 --> 00:45:16,420
kako bi ovaj pederko sutra
glumio da ga ia 20 minuta.

482
00:45:17,020 --> 00:45:19,100
Ali modeli se
biraju iz eira.

483
00:45:19,820 --> 00:45:22,300
Kako e Louis dobiti ba
njega ako je odabir sluajan?

484
00:45:22,500 --> 00:45:26,260
Ime njihove ekipe nije
u eiru, ve kod njega.

485
00:45:26,460 --> 00:45:29,420
Tijekom izbora zavui e
ruku u dep, hokus-pokus...

486
00:45:29,540 --> 00:45:31,340
I Louisu e pripasti riokosi.

487
00:45:36,420 --> 00:45:38,620
Lijepo, Raymonde.

488
00:45:40,100 --> 00:45:41,300
Christina?

489
00:45:42,020 --> 00:45:43,620
Pazi!

490
00:45:50,740 --> 00:45:53,220
Da? -ivni malo, vodimo.

491
00:45:53,820 --> 00:45:58,660
Trebamo samo blagu
nijansu. Tako diskretnu

492
00:45:59,020 --> 00:46:02,020
da se ne primijeti da
je bojana. Nita lake.

493
00:46:02,220 --> 00:46:04,100
Ovaj je bar iv.

494
00:46:05,180 --> 00:46:08,140
Je li ovo prema pravilima?
-Prema mojima jest.

495
00:46:08,860 --> 00:46:11,540
Hajde, rekla si
da eli vjebati.

496
00:46:14,540 --> 00:46:16,180
to radi?

497
00:46:16,460 --> 00:46:18,700
Nije ba presretna.

498
00:46:19,460 --> 00:46:21,220
Svejedno e to uiniti.

499
00:46:29,740 --> 00:46:31,620
Svia mu se ona.

500
00:46:33,700 --> 00:46:36,700
Slomit e mu srce,
ako ve nije.

501
00:46:37,380 --> 00:46:39,460
Tako to ide u ovom poslu.

502
00:46:40,980 --> 00:46:43,540
Da. Valjda.

503
00:46:47,380 --> 00:46:50,900
Tko tebe ia? -Nitko. Sam.

504
00:46:51,220 --> 00:46:54,660
Tako i izgleda.
-Nitko me ne ia.

505
00:46:56,140 --> 00:47:00,380
Ja sam te neko iala. -Ali
sam nauio lekciju, zar ne?

506
00:47:04,580 --> 00:47:07,380
Mogla si bar otii
s drugim tipom.

507
00:47:08,900 --> 00:47:11,860
Za mene nije bilo drugih.

508
00:47:15,380 --> 00:47:17,100
I jo uvijek nema.

509
00:47:20,300 --> 00:47:22,980
Gubite se, lopovi prokleti!

510
00:47:25,820 --> 00:47:28,220
Kradete mi ovce, ha?

511
00:47:40,220 --> 00:47:42,300
Vrijeme je isteklo.
Gotov, zabrljao si.

512
00:47:42,460 --> 00:47:45,300
ike nisi ni taknuo.
Ima samo 20 minuta.

513
00:47:45,660 --> 00:47:48,020
Pet za svaku stranu,
pet straga, tri sprijeda

514
00:47:48,180 --> 00:47:51,300
i dvije za dovravanje.
Mora plesati, mladiu.

515
00:47:51,620 --> 00:47:54,380
Naprijed-natrag,
30 puta u minuti.

516
00:47:55,300 --> 00:47:57,660
Nikad ne bih rekao da mi
sin nee znati plesati.

517
00:47:57,820 --> 00:48:01,060
Po tome si sigurno
na majku. Na prste.

518
00:48:01,300 --> 00:48:03,620
Dri ravnoteu i
krei se. Osjeti to.

519
00:48:09,100 --> 00:48:12,540
Sharon, duo, ustani.
Shelley, sjedni.

520
00:48:13,820 --> 00:48:16,940
Ti si na model za veernju
frizuru, a ne lutka.

521
00:48:17,220 --> 00:48:20,140
Pomozi joj. etku.

522
00:48:22,220 --> 00:48:23,500
Sprej.

523
00:48:23,700 --> 00:48:26,180
tedi joj sekunde,
moda ak i minutu.

524
00:48:26,340 --> 00:48:29,260
A za minutu moe
uiniti mnogo toga. ealj.

525
00:48:37,540 --> 00:48:43,580
Koji je tebi vrag? -Cjeloviti
imid. Marilyn Monroe.

526
00:48:45,660 --> 00:48:49,580
Pa nisam mislio da si mljekar.
-Ne svia ti se. Ne valja mu.

527
00:48:49,740 --> 00:48:53,780
Zna li koliko e se Marilyn
Monroe pojaviti sutra?

528
00:48:53,860 --> 00:48:57,580
To je najstariji tos zanata.
-Hajde, nije tako loe.

529
00:48:57,660 --> 00:49:02,420
Boje su dobre, ali...
-Ne. Dobro. Mijenjam pristup.

530
00:49:07,580 --> 00:49:11,380
Mogao bi joj pomoi. Stvarali
ste najbolje imide od svih.

531
00:49:11,620 --> 00:49:16,060
Da neto raistimo. Neu
iati. Pogotovo ne nju.

532
00:49:16,380 --> 00:49:19,740
Dobro. Imid u raditi ja.
lako mi to nikad nije ilo.

533
00:49:20,100 --> 00:49:23,300
Ne znam kako e ukloniti
Rayevog modela iz igre.

534
00:49:23,460 --> 00:49:28,140
Usredotoi se na
posao. Radim na tome.

535
00:49:29,020 --> 00:49:30,780
DRUGA RUNDA
SLOBODNI STIL ZA MUKARCE

536
00:49:43,340 --> 00:49:44,660
Oprosti, prijatelju.

537
00:50:00,060 --> 00:50:03,140
Kako ide, Tony? -Sjajno.

538
00:50:05,100 --> 00:50:07,260
Bez brige. Napunit e se.

539
00:50:07,620 --> 00:50:08,940
Uivaj.

540
00:50:11,700 --> 00:50:15,700
Na modelu br. 9
radit e Hair Montage.

541
00:50:16,980 --> 00:50:18,860
Na modelu broj...
Mogu li vidjeti broj?

542
00:50:18,980 --> 00:50:22,500
Na modelu br. 11
radit e Kilburn Kutters.

543
00:50:22,860 --> 00:50:26,740
Model br. 26...
The Cut Above.

544
00:50:27,780 --> 00:50:29,820
Ne mogu vjerovati.

545
00:50:32,380 --> 00:50:36,020
Model br. 31...
The Cutting Room.

546
00:50:37,660 --> 00:50:39,580
Model broj... Mogu
li vidjeti karticu?

547
00:50:39,660 --> 00:50:42,140
Br. 13. The Flair Hair Salon.

548
00:50:43,820 --> 00:50:47,220
Model br. 17...
The Clip Joint.

549
00:50:47,980 --> 00:50:50,420
Model broj... Mogu
li vidjeti va broj?

550
00:50:50,740 --> 00:50:54,140
Br. 7, hvala. Komu
ete vi pripasti?

551
00:50:54,820 --> 00:50:56,500
Samo hrabro.

552
00:50:58,340 --> 00:51:02,620
Hvala. Model br. 17...
The Style Warriors.

553
00:51:04,100 --> 00:51:06,500
I model broj... Okrenite
ga kako treba. Hvala.

554
00:51:06,740 --> 00:51:11,660
Model br. 19...
Raymondov frizerski studio.

555
00:51:16,660 --> 00:51:17,860
Sjednite.

556
00:51:19,100 --> 00:51:22,940
Model broj 29.
The Main Line. Hvala.

557
00:51:24,900 --> 00:51:29,100
Natjecanje u slobodnom
stilu samo to nije poelo.

558
00:51:32,700 --> 00:51:36,060
Ubija me neizvjesnost.
-Neto bi trebalo.

559
00:51:37,220 --> 00:51:40,180
Imate 20 minuta. Vrijeme...

560
00:51:41,660 --> 00:51:44,340
Sad! Ponimo!

561
00:51:50,660 --> 00:51:52,860
Ima kondoma?

562
00:52:00,460 --> 00:52:02,580
Imam lou vijest
za tvoju bradu.

563
00:52:07,700 --> 00:52:09,180
Zdravo, Noah.

564
00:52:11,420 --> 00:52:16,580
Mislio sam da si u gradu. -Ne
smijem. Tata mi je zabranio...

565
00:52:18,060 --> 00:52:19,540
Zna.

566
00:52:24,460 --> 00:52:27,900
Stvarno mi je ao zbog
kose ujaka vaega oca.

567
00:52:31,100 --> 00:52:33,740
Nadam se da se on smije tomu.

568
00:52:34,260 --> 00:52:35,980
Jadnik.

569
00:52:39,660 --> 00:52:41,580
Teko je iati ovce.

570
00:52:42,940 --> 00:52:46,460
Ne znam zato se trudimo.
Ionako e nas opljakati.

571
00:52:47,020 --> 00:52:51,900
Zar ne razlikujete svoje
ovce od tuih? -Sve su sline.

572
00:52:54,500 --> 00:52:57,940
Mogla bih vam pomoi.
Ako mi dopustite.

573
00:53:03,220 --> 00:53:07,340
20 minuta je prolo.
Odloite kare.

574
00:53:07,900 --> 00:53:10,140
Odloite ih.

575
00:53:12,820 --> 00:53:16,860
Ako smijem dodati, dame i
gospodo... Zar nisu divni?

576
00:53:35,460 --> 00:53:39,980
FRIZERSKE BORBE
SE ZAGRIJAVAJU

577
00:53:40,620 --> 00:53:44,180
Pokuala sam te zvati.
Ali signal je ovdje lo.

578
00:53:44,460 --> 00:53:48,660
Deacone... Da, ja sam za.

579
00:53:49,860 --> 00:53:51,460
Pa-pa.

580
00:53:58,980 --> 00:54:01,300
ula sam da si zablistao
u slobodnom stilu.

581
00:54:01,500 --> 00:54:03,260
Gdje si bila?

582
00:54:03,540 --> 00:54:06,380
Ne smijem naputati
farmu osim kao model.

583
00:54:07,420 --> 00:54:09,300
Ali imala sam posla.

584
00:54:09,740 --> 00:54:11,860
Skuila sam kako
se boji. Zbilja.

585
00:54:11,980 --> 00:54:13,420
Da? -Da.

586
00:54:22,860 --> 00:54:26,340
Bojanje ti ide sve bolje.
-Ruiasta mi jo ne ide.

587
00:54:26,700 --> 00:54:30,740
Skida se. -Dobro si obojila
i onog riokosog sino.

588
00:54:37,460 --> 00:54:39,220
To je bila tatina ideja.

589
00:54:41,500 --> 00:54:44,300
Briane, to je samo kosa.

590
00:54:46,380 --> 00:54:49,020
Ali vrijedi varati da
bi se osvojio naslov, ha?

591
00:54:53,300 --> 00:54:57,020
Vidimo se. -Briane...

592
00:55:04,660 --> 00:55:08,380
Nakon slobodnog stila vodi
Raymondov frizerski studio,

593
00:55:08,900 --> 00:55:12,260
slijede Kilburn Kutters...
-Jasmine, razmiljao sam...

594
00:55:14,900 --> 00:55:16,140
to?

595
00:55:20,420 --> 00:55:22,060
To je bila Vincentova ideja.

596
00:55:24,620 --> 00:55:28,180
Sharon, mora se smijeiti
za veernju frizuru.

597
00:55:29,060 --> 00:55:33,980
Ne, mora se smijeiti vie.
Suci to vole. Izgleda ljepe.

598
00:55:40,820 --> 00:55:42,900
Cjelovit imid.

599
00:55:48,020 --> 00:55:50,580
Aha. Lijepo.

600
00:55:55,020 --> 00:55:57,020
U emu je problem, jebote?

601
00:55:57,780 --> 00:55:59,580
Ima neto rei?

602
00:56:01,100 --> 00:56:03,820
Nemam. Hajde, da ujem.

603
00:56:04,580 --> 00:56:08,980
Elegancija, domiljatost
i mata. To suci trae.

604
00:56:09,140 --> 00:56:12,100
Znai, hoe rei da nisam
elegantna i domiljata?

605
00:56:12,340 --> 00:56:16,940
Izgleda kao pantomimiarka.
-Pa ti si strunjak, je li?

606
00:56:17,460 --> 00:56:22,340
Zato mi ne pomogne?
-Dobro zna zato.

607
00:56:30,060 --> 00:56:31,980
Phile, zar ba mora?

608
00:56:32,500 --> 00:56:35,340
etvrti ste, a ekaju
vas jo dvije runde.

609
00:56:35,580 --> 00:56:38,020
Jedva da postoje
izgledi da pobijedite.

610
00:56:38,220 --> 00:56:41,940
Ali neete uspjeti
ovakvim cjelovitim imidem.

611
00:56:42,140 --> 00:56:44,300
Bez tebe sigurno neemo.

612
00:56:51,660 --> 00:56:53,460
Odmah se vraam, Shaz.

613
00:57:08,980 --> 00:57:10,500
Jesi dobro, duo?

614
00:57:17,100 --> 00:57:20,780
Oprosti, Sandra. ao mi je.

615
00:57:21,500 --> 00:57:25,980
Laljivice. Prokleta
laljivice. -Sand!

616
00:57:27,580 --> 00:57:29,180
Svi van.

617
00:57:30,260 --> 00:57:34,020
Zar nemate kamo?
Briite! -Stani, Sandra.

618
00:57:36,700 --> 00:57:38,620
Znao si, zar ne?

619
00:57:39,780 --> 00:57:43,060
Naravno da jesi.
I ti, Phile.

620
00:57:44,660 --> 00:57:47,460
Izdajice. Svi ste znali
osim blesave krave.

621
00:57:47,700 --> 00:57:51,020
Nemojte joj rei. Ona joj
je samo cura. to ona zna?

622
00:57:51,740 --> 00:57:54,260
Sandra... -Da se nisi usudio!

623
00:57:54,700 --> 00:57:58,620
Nakon 10 g. utnje doe ovamo
i kae mi da nisam elegantna.

624
00:57:58,820 --> 00:58:01,020
E pa ima pravo. Nisam!

625
00:58:01,380 --> 00:58:04,860
Ali imam cipelu i nabit u
te u guzicu. Gubi se odavde.

626
00:58:05,140 --> 00:58:08,460
Van! I ti, van iz moje radnje.

627
00:58:09,580 --> 00:58:13,180
A moji pramenovi? -Jebali
te pramenovi, mar van!

628
00:58:26,620 --> 00:58:30,740
Pramenovi e pozelenjeti ako
ih ostavi predugo. -Koliko?

629
00:58:31,580 --> 00:58:33,180
Ovoliko.

630
00:58:34,420 --> 00:58:38,540
Naite si novoga
modela za sutra. Kvragu!

631
00:58:39,460 --> 00:58:41,340
Tuit u vas.

632
00:58:42,180 --> 00:58:45,900
Daj, Sandra... Ljubavi...

633
00:58:46,140 --> 00:58:51,580
Rekla si da si ista.
Rekla si... Kvragu.

634
00:59:20,180 --> 00:59:24,180
Hitan recept.
Analgetici dr. Hamiltona.

635
00:59:25,740 --> 00:59:27,940
Moga prijatelja Boba.

636
00:59:31,940 --> 00:59:34,500
Jesi li donijela
onaj fini ampon?

637
00:59:35,500 --> 00:59:38,260
Glupo vrijeme za frizuru.

638
00:59:38,580 --> 00:59:41,100
Daisy? to radite budni?

639
00:59:41,260 --> 00:59:44,580
Sa slinavcima sam
i umiruima. Buni su.

640
00:59:45,180 --> 00:59:47,380
No je jedino mirno doba dana.

641
00:59:47,740 --> 00:59:50,100
Nema kare sa sobom, zar ne?

642
00:59:50,620 --> 00:59:55,660
Kosa mi se plete kad se ne
ia redovito. Gnjavim te.

643
00:59:56,940 --> 00:59:59,780
Doi u sutra, Daisy.
Donijet u sve to treba.

644
00:59:59,980 --> 01:00:03,420
Doi u sutra. Svi to kau...

645
01:00:04,900 --> 01:00:09,180
A nikad ne dou. A ja nemam
jo mnogo dana pred sobom.

646
01:00:09,380 --> 01:00:13,340
Ako si zaboravila, nemam
ni ja, vjetice sebina.

647
01:00:17,620 --> 01:00:19,700
Tako treba.

648
01:00:24,540 --> 01:00:26,180
Onda sutra.

649
01:00:26,900 --> 01:00:28,740
TREA RUNDA
VEERNJA FRIZURA

650
01:00:35,500 --> 01:00:37,340
Dame i gospodo,

651
01:00:38,900 --> 01:00:42,060
dobrodoli natrag na frizersko
prvenstvo u Keighleyju!

652
01:00:42,340 --> 01:00:47,820
Dobro, ljepotice,
na pozornicu! Hvala.

653
01:00:51,260 --> 01:00:54,060
Trea runda zove se
Veernja frizura.

654
01:00:54,380 --> 01:00:57,220
U njoj suci trae

655
01:00:57,460 --> 01:01:00,460
frizuru za veernji
izlazak koja objedinjuje

656
01:01:00,700 --> 01:01:04,220
elegantni tradicionalizam s
matovitim modernim pristupom

657
01:01:04,420 --> 01:01:07,620
sveanom stilu odijevanja.
Tako pie ovdje.

658
01:01:07,900 --> 01:01:11,660
Znai, fina frizura za
petak naveer, zar ne?

659
01:01:12,660 --> 01:01:14,580
A da pitamo nekoga, tata?

660
01:01:15,340 --> 01:01:17,380
Bilo koga. Ne moemo
samo tako odustati.

661
01:01:17,620 --> 01:01:20,140
ak i da imamo modela, nikad
nisam volio veernje frizure.

662
01:01:20,340 --> 01:01:23,340
To je specijalnost
tvoje majke. I Raya.

663
01:01:24,020 --> 01:01:25,700
Mogli smo ih pobijediti.

664
01:01:41,540 --> 01:01:43,580
Pourite se i sjednite, dame.

665
01:01:49,900 --> 01:01:53,140
Sudionici dravnoga
frizerskog prvenstva,

666
01:01:53,700 --> 01:01:59,180
imate 45 minuta.
Neka ianje pone!

667
01:02:01,780 --> 01:02:07,220
to emo danas? -Neto
posebno. Neto otmjeno.

668
01:02:08,100 --> 01:02:09,420
Moe.

669
01:02:25,780 --> 01:02:28,940
Kaem ti, samo je
izaao. Bez rijei.

670
01:02:29,140 --> 01:02:33,020
Nije ni taknuo jaja.
-Vratit e se, dobro?

